23/acs/acs-55.html)\n","- [ACS/Census Data of Household Income](https://www.census.gov/topics/income-poverty/income/data/tables.html)\n","- [Ohio's Higher Ed Campuses](https://highered.ohio.gov/about/ohios-campuses)"],"metadata":{"id":"18_wUBkIZ6fo"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### **Expected Outcomes**\n","\n","1. A cleaned dataset for the population of Ohio at census tract level which may include the following fields:\n","    - Block group ID (GEOID)\n","    - Census tract ID (GEOID)\n","    - County name\n","    - Metropolitan area name\n","    - Population in 18-24 age group (2010, 2020)\n","    - Per capita Population in 18-24 age group (2010, 2020)\n","    - Per capita population change in 18-24 age group from 2010 to 2020\n","    - Count of households with a size <= 2 (2010, 2020)\n","    - Percentage of household with a size <= 2 (2010, 2020)\n","    - Per capita households with a size <= 2 (2010, 2020)\n","    - Median household income (2010, 2020)\n","2. A series of maps which showcase: (1) the boundaries of college towns in Ohio and their names; (2) selected metrics which support your choice of boundaries; and (3) the patterns of demographic change in college towns using appropriate visual variables (color, size, symbolization, etc.)\n","3. A final report describing the patterns of change and addressing potential drivers behind those patterns (consider comparing demographic factors such as age, income, etc.)"],"metadata":{"id":"sRut-06abzwo"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":["### **Visualization Examples**\n","\n","- [Exploring Age Groups in the 2020 Census](https://www.census.gov/library/visualizations/interactive/exploring-age-groups-in-the-2020-census.html)\n","\n","![img](https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1FiUWuyH3fnL-uiw0kvm6bidCAtsDgwwg)\n","\n","- [U.S. Census percentage of people enrolled in college](https://www.arcgis.com/home/item.html?id=3b15603a72e74c20a66b724952c3fbac)\n","\n","![img](https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view